==Sirius Award== The Sirius Award has been created to recognise Australia's emerging actors, modelled on the [[Berlin Film Festival]]'s Shooting Stars initiative. In 2015 [[Mark Coles Smith]] and [[Odessa Young]] won the award.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://if.com.au/2015/11/23/article/New-award-for-Australias-rising-stars/SBDEEFWBNZ.html|title=New award for Australia's rising stars|accessdate=31 December 2016}}</ref> In 2016 the Sirius Award were given to [[Katherine Langford]] and Jacob Collins Levy.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/castingguildofaustralia/photos/a.880398898645435.1073741830.815634601788532/1352130698138917/?type=3&theater|title=Sirisu Awards 2016|accessdate=7 August 2017}}</ref>
