{{Multiple issues| {{Orphan|date=January 2017}} {{unreferenced|date=February 2015}} }}
'''Seefood TV''' is a [[Norwegian culture|Norwegian]] [[production company]] for television and film. They produce for the Norwegian broadcasters [[TV 2 (Norway)|TV2]], [[TVNorge]] og [[NRK]]. They also produce commercial film. The company was founded in 2001 by [[Kristian Ødegård]] og [[Espen Eckbo]] and their first production was the reality parody Santas In A Barn. The company has produced several award winning and critically acclaimed comedy series for television.{{citation needed|date=February 2015}}
==Productions== * ''[[Santas In A Barn]]'', comedy series [[TVNorge]] 2001 * ''[[På klozz hold]]'', comedy series [[TVNorge]] 2002 * ''[[Tonight with Timothy Dahle]]'', comedy talkshow [[TV 2 (Norway)|TV2]] 2003 * ''[[TV2-nøttene]]'', comedy quiz [[TV 2 (Norway)|TV2]] 2004-2008 * ''[[Jul i Tøyengata]]'', comedy drama [[TVNorge]] 2006 * ''[[Best of Espen Eckbo]]'', comedy show [[TV 2 (Norway)|TV2]] 2007 * ''[[Lille Nøtteaften]]'', comedy show [[TV 2 (Norway)|TV2]] 2006, 2007 og 2008 * ''[[Det var en gang et eventyr]]'', drama series [[NRK]] 2008 * ''[[Three Through One]]'', comedy drama [[TV 2 (Norway)|TV2]] 2008 * ''[[På hjul med Dag Otto]]'', entertainment [[TV 2 (Norway)|TV2]] 2010 * ''[[Kolonihagen]]'', entertainment [[TV 2 (Norway)|TV2]] 2010 * ''[[Påpp & Råkk]]'', comedy drama [[NRK]] 2010
