'''''Standup in Stilettos''''' is an American [[stand-up comedy]] show that aired on the [[Pop (U.S. TV network)|TV Guide Network]] and was presented by [[Kate Flannery]]. The series premiered on June 16, 2012. The show featured three comedians each episode and they performed for about 7 to 8 minutes each.

